2:T618,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What is mandi khata software?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Mandi khata software is a digital ledger built specifically for mandi traders and commission agents. It replaces paper bahis with a real-time, party-wise khata that updates the moment you record a sale, purchase, advance or payment."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How is MandiGrow khata different from a regular khata book app?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Generic khata apps only record udhar. MandiGrow is a full mandi ledger system: it links every khata entry to the underlying sale, purchase, commission and GST entry — so your books are always tally-clean and audit-ready."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I see all my party balances at once?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. The party balances screen shows every farmer and buyer with their current outstanding, advance, last transaction date and total turnover — sortable and filterable."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does the khata work offline?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes — MandiGrow caches your data locally and syncs as soon as the connection is back. You can record entries from the mandi gate even with patchy mobile data."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I share a party statement on WhatsApp?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Generate any party statement, export as PDF, and share on WhatsApp directly from the app. Bilingual: Hindi or English."}}]}0:{"rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","main",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-[#f7fbf3] text-gray-900","children":[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Hom